def age_bins(df):
       if df["Age"]<=5:
        return "0-5"
       elif df["Age"]<=10 and df['Age']>5:
        return "5-10"
       elif df["Age"]<=15 and df['Age']>10:
        return "10-15"
       else :
        return ">15"
data_train['Age_bins']=data_train.apply(age_bins,axis=1)
